ned editor
==========

simple editor written in Ada

This app is still under construction. Basic editing, loading and saving from and 
to files work. There still are major bugs, if the program crashes you could loose
your data.

build instructions
------------------

The alire build tool is required for building this application. https://alire.ada.dev/

`alr build` should suffice

license and credit
------------------

This application is licenced under the GNU GPL v3

The ANSI terminal code is based on https://github.com/darkestkhan/vt100
